cross: Laeliocattleya Happy Essence x Cattleya walkeriana

measurements.description: Thirteen well-presented flowers on two upright up to 22.5-cm inflorescences; sepals flat, petals lightly ruffled, sepals and petals pale pink; lip ruffled, white, centrally light yellow, edged light pink, throat magenta; column white, anther cap dark pink; substance firm; texture matte.
